<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.8">
<l>ekkālat tentaiyā yeṉṉuṇ maṉṉiṉmaṟ</l>
<l>ṟekkā lattilum yātoṉṟum vēṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>mikkār vēta vimalar viḻuṅkume</l>
<l>ṉakkārak kaṉiyē yuṉṉai yāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Any time you stay in my heart as my father,</l>
<l>during all that time I won’t need anything</l>
<l>from you, my sweet ripe fruit</l>
<l>which the flawless ones who excell in the Vedas swallow.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
